title: About this Website
---
body:

I initially started this website to create a professional profile where I document my learning notes.
A profile that I can use to share ideas and thoughts, and to build on them over time.

But I wanted something more than an online resume... So...

This website is for everything that I am curious about. 
The mundane. In here you will find the ideas that drive me, the things that define me, my environment, experiences, culture... South Africa.
